title: 08/17/21 DPS Hour 3 Is Kawhi a Real Leader?
itunes:title: 08/17/21 DPS Hour 3 Is Kawhi a Real Leader?
description:
Doug Gottlieb and Jason McIntyre, in for Dan, debate whether or not Kawhi Leonard is a true leader or failing to "face the music" when it comes to the Clippers falling short of expectations. Naomi Osaka gets emotional after an exchange with a reporter but was the question really out of order? Plus, Tebow gets cut by the Jaguars after week 1 of the preseason.
